ENDCLASS.



CLASS ZCL_MFP_ACTION_RSN_FORM_FEEDER IMPLEMENTATION.


METHOD ADD_SY_MESSAGE.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_ACTION_RSN_FORM_FEEDER~ADD_SY_MESSAGE
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for the MyFi Admin POWL
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
  DATA: ls_message TYPE fpmgb_s_t100_message.
  CONSTANTS:
    BEGIN OF e_msgty,
      abort   TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'A',
      error   TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'E',
      info    TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'I',
      success TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'S',
      warning TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'W',
      abend   TYPE sy-msgty VALUE 'X',
    END OF e_msgty.
  CONSTANTS:
    BEGIN OF e_severity,
      error   TYPE fpmgb_severity VALUE 'E',
      warning TYPE fpmgb_severity VALUE 'W',
      success TYPE fpmgb_severity VALUE 'S',
    END OF e_severity.

  ls_message-msgid = sy-msgid.
  ls_message-msgno = sy-msgno.
  CASE sy-msgty.
    WHEN e_msgty-info OR e_msgty-success.
      ls_message-severity = e_severity-success.
    WHEN e_msgty-warning.
      ls_message-severity = e_severity-warning.
    WHEN OTHERS.
      ls_message-severity = e_severity-error.
  ENDCASE.
  ls_message-parameter_1 = sy-msgv1.
  ls_message-parameter_2 = sy-msgv2.
  ls_message-parameter_3 = sy-msgv3.
  ls_message-parameter_4 = sy-msgv4.

  ls_message-ref_name = ref_name.
  ls_message-ref_index = ref_index.

  APPEND ls_message TO messages.
ENDMETHOD.


METHOD CLOSE_DIALOG.
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* METHOD ID:          ZCL_MFP_ACTION_RSN_FORM_FEEDER~CLOSE_DIALOG
* DESCRIPTION:        This method is used by the MyFi Purchasing (MFP) UI5
*                     application (Self Service Purchasing (SSP) Release 2).
*                     This method is used for the MyFi Admin POWL
*
* AUTHOR:             Stephen Ning (290977SCN), James Southwell (070667JPS)
* CREATE DATE:        30.05.2020
* R/3 RELEASE VERSION: ECC6
*
* ACTIVITY:           AD-11-32-07 - Self Service Purchasing App
* CR Number:          6000001863 - MyFi Purchasing Release 2
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* VERSION CONTROL
*
* Date     Author    CTS Req    Dev Script     Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
* 30.05.20 290977SCN RD2K919078 DS-11-32-07-01 Created
*          070667JPS
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
  DATA: lr_fpm TYPE REF TO if_fpm.

  lr_fpm = cl_fpm_factory=>get_instance( ).
  lr_fpm->raise_event_by_id( iv_event_id = cl_fpm_event=>gc_event_close_dialog_box ).
ENDMETHOD.


